---
title: Chopped Chicken Salad with Charred Veggies and Avocado-Lime Dressing
description: Velvety avocado creates a delicious (and healthy!) base for this creamy dressing. Spiced chicken is paired with slightly charred peppers and onions to take this chopped chicken salad to the next level.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chopped-romaine-salad-with-avocado-crema-8b4567.jpg
